1
00:00:06,030 --> 00:00:08,464
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,464 --> 00:00:12,119
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,119 --> 00:00:18,212
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,212 --> 00:00:24,538
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,538 --> 00:00:30,917
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,917 --> 00:00:36,045
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,045 --> 00:00:43,245
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,245 --> 00:00:48,269
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,269 --> 00:00:49,882
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,882 --> 00:00:55,645
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,645 --> 00:01:00,545
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:00,545 --> 00:01:07,822
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:07,822 --> 00:01:11,802
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,640
Tiger, don't bark! He's family.

15
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,560
Bin, you're here.

16
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,799
Third Uncle. Where's Anna?

17
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:23,899
Anna's inside the house.

18
00:01:23,899 --> 00:01:25,280
Anna, come out here!

19
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,159
Why did you bring Gao Yang to Third Uncle's house?

20
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,560
Let's talk it out slowly.

21
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:31,080
Third Uncle, you have no idea what Anna did.

22
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:33,840
My dad pulled so many strings to get her the accountant job at the factory!

23
00:01:33,840 --> 00:01:36,319
She just quit it like that! That's an iron rice bowl (secure job)!

24
00:01:36,319 --> 00:01:37,879
What secure job?

25
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,760
You call that a secure job?

26
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:42,319
How many years has that factory been in a deficit? Are you going to support me if I'm laid off?

27
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:44,640
I'll support you. Quickly, go back to the factory now!

28
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:45,920
I don't need you to support me.

29
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,799
Anna, stop saying that.

30
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:50,839
I'm going to tell you one last time. I'm going to Beijing. Are you coming or not?

31
00:01:50,839 --> 00:01:52,399
- I'm not going!
- Let's get a divorce, then!

32
00:01:52,399 --> 00:01:54,120
Fine! Who are you trying to intimidate?

33
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,879
You haven't fought enough at home? Why did you come to show off at Third Uncle's house?

34
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,159
Third Uncle is family.

35
00:01:57,159 --> 00:01:58,239
You be the judge, Third Uncle.

36
00:01:58,239 --> 00:02:00,200
- Is she making sense?
- How am I not making sense?

37
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:02,040
I found you a job and that's your attitude?

38
00:02:02,040 --> 00:02:03,280
No matter what you say today, let me tell you...

39
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,120
Gao Yang ran away!

40
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,699
- What?
- Gao Yang climbed over the wall and ran away!

41
00:02:05,699 --> 00:02:06,400
Gao Yang!

42
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,439
Gao...

43
00:02:07,439 --> 00:02:08,759
Hurry and get a flashlight!

44
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,758
Gao Yang!

45
00:02:09,758 --> 00:02:13,322
[Episode 17: The Night Shooting Stars Failed to Arrive]

46
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,840
Why did this group of kids come here?

47
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:43,019
Third Uncle, it was supposed to be just the two of us.

48
00:02:43,019 --> 00:02:45,059
They just had to come along.

49
00:02:45,059 --> 00:02:47,319
You troublemaker.

50
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:01,920
Which one of you is Gao Yang?

51
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:04,239
Great Third Uncle, I'm Gao Yang.

52
00:03:04,239 --> 00:03:05,759
How can you forget me?

53
00:03:05,759 --> 00:03:07,640
Who is he then?

54
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:10,199
My brother Ye Xiaowen.

55
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:14,159
- You got married again?
- What?

56
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:16,000
Why didn't you tell me?

57
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,579
I didn't even prepare a red envelope.

58
00:03:18,579 --> 00:03:20,360
Third Uncle, you've mistaken.

59
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:22,199
He is my student. I'm coaching him.

60
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:24,199
Hello, Great Third Uncle.

61
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:32,860
Wait, Third Uncle. Is it too much trouble?

62
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:36,439
If it's too much trouble, we'll go home.

63
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:39,240
It's no trouble. It's nice to have so many guests.

64
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:40,879
Your Third Aunt-in-Law went to visit the children in the city.

65
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:44,139
I can talk to people instead of the dog now.

66
00:03:44,139 --> 00:03:47,280
Go inside the house and have some cucumbers. I'll go and slaughter a pig.

67
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:48,599
That's all right, Great Third Uncle.

68
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:51,839
There's no need! Th-there's no need to slaughter a big one!

69
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,840
Did you guys see that? Great Third Uncle's TV is really big!

70
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:57,680
This place is really nice.

71
00:03:57,680 --> 00:04:00,360
You hillbilly. It's a new countryside now.

72
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:03,599
The villages have better living conditions than the cities now.

73
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:04,759
You don't know anything.

74
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:06,080
Exactly.

75
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,520
You're right.

76
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,560
I was so scared just now.

77
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:11,379
I thought Great Third Uncle wouldn't welcome us here.

78
00:04:12,039 --> 00:04:16,360
Let me tell you, be on your best behavior. Your best behavior, do you understand?

79
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:18,199
Great Third Uncle loves obedient children.

80
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,560
You must have been a naughty child when you were little.

81
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,439
Eat your cucumber.

82
00:04:21,439 --> 00:04:24,920
Gao Yang, I'm here to train. Why are you here?

83
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,480
I'm here to supervise Gao Bin.

84
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,080
Did you forget?

85
00:04:28,080 --> 00:04:31,779
I'm the leader of the track and field team.

86
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,339
Don't worry. It won't affect my grades.

87
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:38,920
What about you guys?

88
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,439
We're here on vacation.

89
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,859
I came to find inspiration for my writing.

90
00:04:42,859 --> 00:04:45,160
I was the spokesperson for agricultural products in the Dadianzi Village.

91
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:47,399
I can be your tour guide.

92
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:52,459
Meng, are you still going to eat your cucumber?

93
00:04:52,459 --> 00:04:53,839
No, here you go.

94
00:04:53,839 --> 00:04:55,639
Thank you.

95
00:04:57,079 --> 00:04:58,579
It's so sweet.

96
00:04:58,579 --> 00:05:01,040
Xiaowen, Mi Jia, go train.

97
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:04,319
Gao Bin, coach them well. Pull out all your tricks, okay?

98
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:07,000
After I finish this cucumber, I'll go supervise you.

99
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:09,320
What does it have to do with you?

100
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:12,120
Good luck, Mr. Gao! Good luck, Xiaowen! Good luck, Jia Jia!

101
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,260
We'll go watch you train in a while.

102
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:19,360
Okay. I'll take you guys sightseeing then.

103
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:29,720
The natural breeze feels so nice.

104
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:32,339
Yes. The wind is so unrestrained.

105
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:35,360
Why must we feel the wind here?

106
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:37,480
Aren't we here on vacation?

107
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,360
Beibei, you should exercise.

108
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:41,659
Watch and learn. Keep up with my rhythm.

109
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,959
What are you doing? Are you going on a stroll?

110
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:45,759
Start running.

111
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:48,359
You're here to supervise Xiaowen. Why are you rushing us?

112
00:05:48,359 --> 00:05:50,959
Aren't you an amateur who loves to instruct an expert?

113
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:52,560
I'll show you what an expert looks like.

114
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,079
Quickly speed up.

115
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:56,000
Can't you just let us watch on the side?

116
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:59,160
Exactly, Uncle Gao. We can just watch.

117
00:05:59,160 --> 00:06:01,399
Fine, watch then.

118
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:47,960
This natural wind is too harsh.

119
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,959
It had shackled both my legs.

120
00:06:49,959 --> 00:06:53,919
That Tiger is such a good runner.

121
00:06:53,919 --> 00:06:55,240
Yeah, right.

122
00:06:55,240 --> 00:07:00,960
It's because you three don't normally exercise much and have poor physical fitness.

123
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,720
Gao Bin, is that it?

124
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,839
End of warmups.

125
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:09,719
The training officially starts now.

126
00:07:09,719 --> 00:07:11,240
I'll give you another choice.

127
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:15,939
If you don't want to train, you can go back and do chores for Third Uncle.

128
00:07:15,939 --> 00:07:16,920
We'll do chores!

129
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:19,039
We'll do chores! We'll do chores! Let's go!

130
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:20,839
Beibei, Beibei.

131
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,639
Slow down! Slow down!

132
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:26,319
I'll take them both back.

133
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,360
Jiabao, take Tiger home.

134
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,319
I'd rather not.

135
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:33,339
It's okay. He doesn't bite.

136
00:07:34,319 --> 00:07:36,319
Be good.

137
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:39,139
Slow down!

138
00:07:39,139 --> 00:07:43,499
- Jia Jia, you train like this every day?
- Yes.

139
00:07:43,499 --> 00:07:46,439
How do you keep this up?

140
00:07:46,439 --> 00:07:49,800
If you train every day, it w-won't be as tiring.

141
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:53,619
I really admire you, Jia Jia.

142
00:07:54,319 --> 00:07:55,560
How is it?

143
00:07:55,560 --> 00:07:57,360
Can you continue?

144
00:08:03,199 --> 00:08:04,240
Let me take a break.

145
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,560
Well, Great Uncle needs me.

146
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:07,979
I'll go help him do chores later.

147
00:08:10,839 --> 00:08:13,079
Xiaowen, are you ready?

148
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,779
Let's begin.

149
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:21,530
If you want to get into the national competition and be in the top three,

150
00:08:21,530 --> 00:08:23,780
you need to at least reach the standards of a Class 1 athlete.

151
00:08:23,780 --> 00:08:26,240
Your current time is 40 seconds over.

152
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:29,979
We need to achieve that goal within one year.

153
00:08:29,979 --> 00:08:32,360
Mi Jia has the provincial boot camp.

154
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:35,539
You have my special training.

155
00:08:35,539 --> 00:08:37,628
Don't slouch. Use the sole of your feet to generate force.

156
00:08:37,628 --> 00:08:40,622
♫  And put the whole world into my head  ♫

157
00:08:40,622 --> 00:08:43,140
If you want to run faster, it's not enough to just train really hard.

158
00:08:43,140 --> 00:08:44,879
♫  To do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

159
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:47,130
First of all, you need to adjust your running posture.

160
00:08:47,130 --> 00:08:48,380
♫ Don't say goodbye ♫

161
00:08:48,380 --> 00:08:52,524
♫  Don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

162
00:08:53,382 --> 00:08:55,799
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

163
00:08:55,799 --> 00:08:57,940
Pay attention to your arm swings.

164
00:08:58,600 --> 00:09:04,599
With the right posture, you'll get double the results with half the effort.

165
00:09:14,879 --> 00:09:19,240
All right. Don't wake me for anything. Call me when dinner's ready.

166
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:21,960
No, Beibei. You d-don't exercise at all.

167
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,600
Once you exercise, you h-have to massage your muscles.

168
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,860
Otherwise, you will be really sore.

169
00:09:25,860 --> 00:09:27,679
Let me rest for a while.

170
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:30,299
Give Meng a massage first.

171
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,399
Th-that's fine, too.

172
00:09:33,399 --> 00:09:35,320
No, no! No, no need!

173
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,679
Why must women make it difficult for fellow women?

174
00:09:36,679 --> 00:09:38,519
Let me give you a massage.

175
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:40,639
"The sharp edge of a sword comes from sharpening.

176
00:09:40,639 --> 00:09:43,819
The aroma of plum blossom comes from the bitter cold" (good results come from hard work).

177
00:09:43,819 --> 00:09:45,200
What's wrong, Meng?

178
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,679
Why are you reciting a poem?

179
00:09:46,679 --> 00:09:48,579
Does it hurt?

180
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,959
It doesn't hurt. It feels quite good, really.

181
00:09:53,959 --> 00:09:56,719
Then give me a massage, too.

182
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,000
Come on.

183
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:34,640
I'll grind the soy beans. You go give Tiger a shower.

184
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:37,199
Great Third Uncle loves Tiger the most.

185
00:10:37,199 --> 00:10:42,259
If you don't clean him well, Great Third Uncle will be mad. Quickly go on now.

186
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,240
Gao Yang, you can't handle such a heavy task. Let me do it.

187
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,080
No, no. I love heavy tasks.

188
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,520
- No, you can't do it. Let me!
- No, no.

189
00:10:48,520 --> 00:10:50,480
Look, you're closer to Tiger. You do it.

190
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:52,519
No, no, stop.

191
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:55,879
What's it doing?

192
00:11:01,519 --> 00:11:04,420
T-Tiger, are you thirsty?

193
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:08,100
Gao Yang, grind him a bowl of soymilk.

194
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:10,899
Gao Yang? Gao Yang!

195
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:14,600
Gao Yang! Gao Yang!

196
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,440
What happened to Gao Yang?

197
00:11:16,879 --> 00:11:18,779
Well... That...

198
00:11:18,779 --> 00:11:22,020
Gao Yang is afraid of the dog. I... I'm comforting him.

199
00:11:22,020 --> 00:11:25,000
Xiaowen, Great Third Uncle told you to give Tiger a shower soon.

200
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:28,380
- Otherwise, he will be mad. Hurry up and go do it.
- Okay.

201
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:33,159
Tiger, let's go. Let's go take a shower.

202
00:11:38,899 --> 00:11:41,819
Welcome to the Dadianzi Village, Everyone.

203
00:11:41,819 --> 00:11:44,280
- Thank you, Great Third Uncle.
- Thank you, Great Third Uncle!

204
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,220
You're welcome.

205
00:11:49,600 --> 00:11:51,500
- Let's eat, Everyone.
- Okay.

206
00:11:51,500 --> 00:11:53,159
Try my cooking.

207
00:11:53,159 --> 00:11:56,100
- It tastes good!
- It's delicious, it's delicious!

208
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:59,799
Gao Yang, are you still afraid of dogs?

209
00:11:59,799 --> 00:12:00,720
I was never afraid of dogs.

210
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:04,339
Is that so? You ran so fast we could see your afterimage just now.

211
00:12:04,339 --> 00:12:07,399
Tiger is very civilized. He doesn't bite.

212
00:12:07,399 --> 00:12:09,160
Yes, yes.

213
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,639
Were you bitten by a dog before when you were younger?

214
00:12:10,639 --> 00:12:13,880
No, no. That happened so many years ago. Let's eat.

215
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:15,479
Delicious.

216
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,796
I still remember what happened years ago.

217
00:12:18,796 --> 00:12:21,639
I've never seen any child as naughty as Gao Yang.

218
00:12:21,639 --> 00:12:26,039
Back then, he didn't even care about his parents arguing over their divorce.

219
00:12:26,039 --> 00:12:32,254
He climbed over the wall in the middle of the night, was chased by a dog, ran for 2 li (1km), and fell into a ditch.

220
00:12:32,254 --> 00:12:35,440
We dragged him out and he ran away again.

221
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:39,639
I was just so confused. Gao Yang, what was so interesting out there?

222
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:42,040
Third Uncle, I remember that as well.

223
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:45,900
Gao Yang, tell us about it. What did you do out there at the time?

224
00:12:45,900 --> 00:12:47,830
Nothing, nothing. Quickly eat your food.

225
00:12:47,839 --> 00:12:51,579
Don't bring up that old story again. Let's eat. Eat your food.

226
00:12:51,579 --> 00:12:52,760
- Come on. Eat up.
- Thank you.

227
00:12:52,760 --> 00:12:54,879
- Have some chicken gizzard.
- Come on.

228
00:12:55,559 --> 00:12:58,459
Little Celebrity! Where's the little celebrity?

229
00:12:58,459 --> 00:13:01,200
- Village Head, why are you here?
- He's over here!

230
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:04,439
- Little Celebrity, nice to meet you.
- Hello.

231
00:13:04,439 --> 00:13:05,799
I have to thank you.

232
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:11,240
Ever since you endorsed our village, the sales of our agricultural products increased drastically.

233
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,519
It's mainly because the quality of our village's agricultural products is good.

234
00:13:13,519 --> 00:13:14,720
You really flatter us.

235
00:13:14,720 --> 00:13:15,600
- How about this?
- Stinky Jiabao!

236
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:18,539
I still have a few more products that I've prepared for you to try. Come with me.

237
00:13:18,539 --> 00:13:21,420
- That... That...
- How about this? Well, I'll be taking him away.

238
00:13:21,420 --> 00:13:23,359
Lunch is on me.

239
00:13:23,359 --> 00:13:24,780
- Let's go.
- Okay.

240
00:13:24,780 --> 00:13:26,960
- You guys enjoy. I'll go with them first.
- Enjoy your food!

241
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:27,759
Enjoy your food!

242
00:13:27,759 --> 00:13:29,860
- You have a few more agricultural products, right?
- Yes, that's right.

243
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:32,379
- Okay.
- Let's go.

244
00:13:32,379 --> 00:13:35,100
So, he's the one who endorsed the sweet potatoes.

245
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:38,579
Third Uncle, he's my student.

246
00:13:38,579 --> 00:13:41,459
Great Third Uncle, he's my classmate.

247
00:13:42,679 --> 00:13:44,720
Come on, let's eat. Here.

248
00:13:44,720 --> 00:13:46,960
Where did you go back then?

249
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:50,199
Nowhere, nowhere. Hurry up and eat.

250
00:14:04,000 --> 00:14:06,780
Enjoy farm-style cuisine during the day,

251
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,919
soak in a hot spring at night.

252
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:13,000
Hanging out with you both is the life I desire.

253
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:17,680
Beibei, what did you tell your dad?

254
00:14:17,680 --> 00:14:21,520
Did you just directly tell him we're going to a hot spring?

255
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:23,320
Of course not!

256
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:26,819
I told my dad I'm going to Meng's house to study.

257
00:14:26,819 --> 00:14:29,100
Th-Then what about Meng? What did you say?

258
00:14:29,100 --> 00:14:33,959
I said I'm going to Beibei's house to tutor her.

259
00:14:33,959 --> 00:14:37,940
Well... Th-they're n-not going to find out, right?

260
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:44,220
No, they won't. I made an elaborate and detailed plan for our girl's trip this time.

261
00:14:46,399 --> 00:14:51,059
Jia Jia, come in here. It's really comfortable!

262
00:14:51,059 --> 00:14:53,799
I-I'll do it later.

263
00:14:53,799 --> 00:14:55,499
Why?

264
00:14:56,840 --> 00:14:59,339
Is Jia shy?

265
00:14:59,339 --> 00:15:03,799
- How about this? Let's cover our eyes and give her some privacy.
- Okay.

266
00:15:03,799 --> 00:15:05,420
Come on.

267
00:15:06,960 --> 00:15:08,560
Alright now.

268
00:15:39,759 --> 00:15:43,720
Mi Jia, why... why haven't we noticed it before?

269
00:15:44,799 --> 00:15:49,160
I-I-I usually wear tight-fitting clothes.

270
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:50,759
So...

271
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:56,539
I'm the one with the smallest ones?

272
00:15:56,539 --> 00:15:58,639
Meng!

273
00:15:59,299 --> 00:16:01,240
That... Do you want some hot spring eggs?

274
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,140
Yes.

275
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,920
Do you girls want some?

276
00:16:06,538 --> 00:16:07,960
What are you doing?

277
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:13,100
Gao Yang, what are you doing? Get out! This is for girls only!

278
00:16:13,100 --> 00:16:15,279
What are you doing? Do you want it or not?

279
00:16:15,279 --> 00:16:18,259
Get out! Get out! Hurry up!

280
00:16:18,259 --> 00:16:25,659
- What are you doing?
- Hurry up! Get out! Get out! Hurry up! You saw us! You saw everything!

281
00:16:25,659 --> 00:16:27,320
What a psycho.

282
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:31,559
Meng, how do you write shy again?

283
00:16:32,559 --> 00:16:35,600
Hello, Ms. Meng. Sister Tian Meng is showering right now.

284
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:38,740
We studied all day. We'll be going to sleep soon.

285
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:41,720
Do you need her to call you back?

286
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:45,899
That's not necessary? Good night, Ms. Meng.

287
00:17:01,930 --> 00:17:05,960
Jin Doudou! You're pouring beer by yourself at home? What do you think you're doing?

288
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:08,620
What's going on? Why are you alone? Where's your sister?

289
00:17:08,620 --> 00:17:15,399
Dad, Mom, you're finally home. I'm so scared to be home alone.

290
00:17:27,559 --> 00:17:32,919
Do you think that since Gao Yang saw me just now, shouldn't he be responsible for me?

291
00:17:40,119 --> 00:17:44,600
Stop drinking. Be honest. What did you see just now?

292
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:47,079
I didn't see anything.

293
00:17:47,079 --> 00:17:49,440
That's not possible. Really?

294
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:51,399
It's true.

295
00:17:51,399 --> 00:17:53,440
Besides,

296
00:17:54,240 --> 00:17:56,140
what is there to see?

297
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:57,519
You...

298
00:17:59,799 --> 00:18:02,039
What's wrong with me? I'm not a woman?

299
00:18:02,039 --> 00:18:08,780
Yes, you are. By the way, yellow doesn't go with your skin tone. It makes you look tan.

300
00:18:11,079 --> 00:18:13,419
You're so annoying!

301
00:18:17,440 --> 00:18:19,920
Wh-What's wrong with Beibei?

302
00:18:19,920 --> 00:18:23,599
Adolescent girls are a bit more restless.

303
00:18:24,799 --> 00:18:28,799
I didn't ask her to come. She came on her own.

304
00:18:29,279 --> 00:18:31,599
She's already here. What can I do?

305
00:18:32,519 --> 00:18:34,459
Lower your voice.

306
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,399
How am I unreliable?

307
00:18:39,119 --> 00:18:43,819
She's fine. She's having a good time eating meat and soaking in a hot spring.

308
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:46,240
Who is it?

309
00:18:46,240 --> 00:18:48,640
Your dad.

310
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:55,780
Put Beibei on the phone?

311
00:18:57,599 --> 00:19:00,459
The kids are all asleep. Talk to her tomorrow.

312
00:19:06,160 --> 00:19:07,860
Okay.

313
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,939
Your dad said he won't yell at you.

314
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:21,679
Hello, Dad.

315
00:19:45,759 --> 00:19:49,159
I'm not leaving!

316
00:19:51,759 --> 00:19:57,880
I'm not leaving! I'll just live in Great Third Uncle's house!

317
00:19:57,880 --> 00:20:01,799
I don't want to go home!

318
00:20:01,799 --> 00:20:06,100
I don't want to be grounded!

319
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:12,540
Alright, Beibei. It won't come to that.

320
00:20:12,540 --> 00:20:15,319
Just apologize to your dad when you go home.

321
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:19,839
Principal Jin will forgive you. Don't worry.

322
00:20:19,839 --> 00:20:20,920
That's right.

323
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:24,499
If he doesn't forgive you, I'll beg for forgiveness on your behalf.

324
00:20:24,499 --> 00:20:27,700
My words are still worth something to him. Don't cry. Don't cry.

325
00:20:27,700 --> 00:20:33,440
No, my dad is really angry this time.

326
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:36,099
He told me he won't...

327
00:20:36,099 --> 00:20:37,880
he won't let me out of the house during summer vacation anymore.

328
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:42,240
I won't be able to watch the show anymore!

329
00:20:42,720 --> 00:20:44,480
I-I-It's okay.

330
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,980
Beibei,

331
00:20:46,540 --> 00:20:49,419
if you can't go, j-just don't watch it.

332
00:20:49,419 --> 00:20:54,599
No! I was going to get autographs for you.

333
00:20:55,039 --> 00:20:58,840
L-let's n-n-not get them then.

334
00:20:58,840 --> 00:21:03,339
No, I've been preparing for it for so long.

335
00:21:03,339 --> 00:21:05,680
I can't just give up!

336
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:08,119
I can't just go back on my word!

337
00:21:08,119 --> 00:21:13,060
But your dad is already a-angry. J-Just stay at home and study during the s-summer vacation.

338
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:15,900
Do you want it or not?

339
00:21:15,900 --> 00:21:18,360
I-I-I d-don't want it.

340
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:20,000
You...

341
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:24,880
So, I've just been self-sentimental all along?

342
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:27,480
- No.
- How can she be like that?

343
00:21:27,480 --> 00:21:29,960
You... You think you're so great with a big chest?

344
00:21:29,960 --> 00:21:34,139
- I...
- Why are you mocking me? Even you're looking down upon me

345
00:21:34,139 --> 00:21:36,819
and bullying me!

346
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:58,720
Is everything okay?

347
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:00,880
It's nothing. She'll be fine after waking up.

348
00:22:01,519 --> 00:22:03,139
Okay then, room assignments.

349
00:22:03,139 --> 00:22:05,839
Xiaowen, you're training tomorrow. You'll take a room by yourself.

350
00:22:05,839 --> 00:22:09,119
Gao Yang, you, me, and Third Uncle will share a room.

351
00:22:09,119 --> 00:22:10,960
The girls will take the room inside.

352
00:22:10,960 --> 00:22:13,919
That won't work. You snore. I don't want to sleep with you.

353
00:22:13,919 --> 00:22:17,580
How about you share a room with Tiger?

354
00:22:21,079 --> 00:22:24,159
Mr. Gao, let Gao Yang share a room with me.

355
00:22:24,159 --> 00:22:26,040
Fine, fine.

356
00:22:26,519 --> 00:22:29,659
Xiaowen, take the blanket. Don't catch a cold.

357
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:35,519
Wait, wait, is there another room?

358
00:22:35,519 --> 00:22:37,140
There is.

359
00:22:37,140 --> 00:22:40,119
The Village head's house. Go share a room with Jiabao.

360
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:46,980
Let's go. Let's go to sleep. To sleep.

361
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:17,440
What is it? Are you really angry?

362
00:23:18,559 --> 00:23:21,759
It was just the heat of the moment, right?

363
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:25,680
You're not children anymore.

364
00:23:26,799 --> 00:23:29,020
Don't act like this, okay?

365
00:23:30,319 --> 00:23:34,240
I'm not angry. I'm going to sleep.

366
00:23:37,880 --> 00:23:41,419
Beibei, Jia doesn't have any blankets this way.

367
00:23:55,720 --> 00:23:58,879
You can have it. I don't want it anymore.

368
00:23:59,799 --> 00:24:01,599
Jia.

369
00:24:01,599 --> 00:24:03,440
I don't want it either.

370
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:13,100
Third Uncle, are you asleep?

371
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:18,239
- What are you looking for?
- Your Third Aunt-in-Law isn't here. Have a drink with me.

372
00:24:18,239 --> 00:24:20,599
I'm not drinking. I still have to train tomorrow.

373
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,880
Next time, then.

374
00:24:24,880 --> 00:24:26,399
Third Uncle,

375
00:24:29,250 --> 00:24:31,259
just two sips.

376
00:24:46,519 --> 00:24:47,919
Come on.

377
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:55,160
It's only called liquor when two people drink it.

378
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:56,740
Yes, yes.

379
00:24:56,740 --> 00:24:58,480
Come on, have some more.

380
00:24:58,480 --> 00:24:59,839
That's enough for me, Third Uncle.

381
00:24:59,839 --> 00:25:02,860
Alright, that's it for today.

382
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,860
Third Uncle,

383
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:14,359
did Anna buy you that TV?

384
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:17,299
How much was it?

385
00:25:17,299 --> 00:25:19,140
What do you mean how much?

386
00:25:19,140 --> 00:25:20,979
Don't ask.

387
00:25:20,979 --> 00:25:22,440
Just tell me.

388
00:25:22,440 --> 00:25:26,000
I didn't want it. Anna insisted on buying it.

389
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:29,540
It was over 10,000 Yuan. She must've been scammed.

390
00:25:38,400 --> 00:25:40,000
Third Uncle,

391
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:41,600
let's have another drink.

392
00:25:44,599 --> 00:25:46,799
Are you upset?

393
00:25:46,799 --> 00:25:49,400
Let me tell you,

394
00:25:49,400 --> 00:25:51,640
I don't watch TV.

395
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:54,119
For human beings, sentiments are the most important.

396
00:25:54,119 --> 00:25:57,480
Nothing is better than having you come to visit me often.

397
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,280
I know, Third Uncle.

398
00:26:06,200 --> 00:26:10,439
That TV is nothing. It doesn't even cost more than the washing machine.

399
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:15,560
Let's have another drink.

400
00:26:16,039 --> 00:26:17,440
You're not training tomorrow?

401
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:19,040
It won't affect it.

402
00:26:28,940 --> 00:26:31,079
Wh-where's Tiger?

403
00:26:32,559 --> 00:26:34,800
Did he go to the restroom?

404
00:26:35,319 --> 00:26:37,740
Doesn't look like it.

405
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,319
Did he run away?

406
00:26:40,319 --> 00:26:41,919
He ran away?

407
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:45,680
That won't do. Great Third Uncle loves Tiger the most. We have to go look for him.

408
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:48,619
I'll go and get a flashlight. W-Wait for me.

409
00:26:51,219 --> 00:26:52,780
Tiger!

410
00:26:52,780 --> 00:26:55,190
Tiger!

411
00:26:55,199 --> 00:26:57,200
Tiger!

412
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:59,340
Tiger!

413
00:27:00,039 --> 00:27:03,400
Xiaowen, you should go back first. You still have to train tomorrow.

414
00:27:03,400 --> 00:27:04,640
I'll look for him myself.

415
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,639
Aren't you afraid of dogs?

416
00:27:06,639 --> 00:27:08,599
I can't let it affect your training though.

417
00:27:08,599 --> 00:27:11,459
- It's all right. Let's hurry and look for him.
- Tiger!

418
00:27:11,459 --> 00:27:13,339
Tiger!

419
00:27:13,339 --> 00:27:14,960
Gao Yang!

420
00:27:15,419 --> 00:27:17,419
Gao Yang!

421
00:27:17,419 --> 00:27:25,791
- Gao Yang! Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang! Gao Yang!

422
00:27:27,300 --> 00:27:31,412
- Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang!

423
00:27:32,839 --> 00:27:34,100
- Gao Yang!
- This way!

424
00:27:34,100 --> 00:27:37,259
This way! Let's look separately!

425
00:27:37,259 --> 00:27:38,900
Gao Yang!

426
00:27:39,880 --> 00:27:44,493
- Gao Yang! Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang!

427
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:46,939
Gao Yang!

428
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:50,100
Gao Yang!

429
00:27:50,740 --> 00:27:53,559
Such a nice family. Why must you split up?

430
00:27:53,559 --> 00:27:54,680
Gao Yang!

431
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:57,200
Why must you go to Beijing?

432
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:59,179
I just don't want Gao Yang to live like this in the future!

433
00:27:59,179 --> 00:28:00,779
Like what?

434
00:28:00,799 --> 00:28:02,980
Like what?

435
00:28:04,119 --> 00:28:08,500
Staying in such a small place where the future is as far as the eyes can see.

436
00:28:08,500 --> 00:28:12,860
Just like Gao Bin, who's happy with the way things are and muddling through life.

437
00:28:12,860 --> 00:28:17,339
When Gao Yang grows up, would he rely on his grandpa or Gao Bin?

438
00:28:17,339 --> 00:28:24,040
The times have changed. If I don't struggle, strive, and work hard, the child will suffer when he grows up.

439
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:27,900
Wouldn't the child still suffer if you two get a divorce?

440
00:28:27,900 --> 00:28:29,620
Third Uncle—

441
00:28:29,620 --> 00:28:33,149
- Gao Yang! Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang!

442
00:28:33,149 --> 00:28:35,140
I'm exhausted.

443
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:42,719
Tiger, what were you doing? Why did you run out in the middle of the night?

444
00:28:42,719 --> 00:28:44,000
I'm so exhausted.

445
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:47,759
Tiger, tell me. Did you learn that from Gao Yang?

446
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:49,900
What do you know?

447
00:28:49,900 --> 00:28:53,480
Back then... I had my reasons back then, okay?

448
00:28:53,480 --> 00:28:55,400
What reason?

449
00:28:56,200 --> 00:28:58,200
There are really shooting stars here.

450
00:29:01,680 --> 00:29:06,100
The air quality in the Dadianzi Village is good. It's normal to see shooting stars.

451
00:29:16,340 --> 00:29:18,040
What's wrong?

452
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:26,999
At the time, I ran out to see shooting stars.

453
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,839
To make a wish?

454
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:40,280
The news broadcast at that time said there would be shooting stars at Dadianzi Village at night.

455
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:44,639
I waited for a long time and didn't see anything.

456
00:29:47,839 --> 00:29:52,820
I ended up falling into a stinky water ditch and got bitten by a dog.

457
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,920
Let's wait for a bit longer.

458
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:02,319
Maybe there would be more.

459
00:30:05,200 --> 00:30:06,800
Even if there are,

460
00:30:10,039 --> 00:30:12,119
it's already too late.

461
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:19,200
Don't run out by yourself again, understand?

462
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:22,939
Do you understand? Do you understand?

463
00:30:22,939 --> 00:30:25,000
Gao Yang, where are you going?

464
00:30:25,000 --> 00:30:26,079
Come back here, Gao Yang!

465
00:30:26,079 --> 00:30:28,860
Come out now, Shooting Star!

466
00:30:28,860 --> 00:30:32,680
Shooting Star, I want to make a wish! Anna and Gao Bin are not allowed to get a divorce!

467
00:30:32,680 --> 00:30:34,960
Come out now, Shooting Star!

468
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:39,419
Shooting Star, I want to make a wish. Anna and Gao Bin are not allowed to get a divorce!

469
00:30:43,419 --> 00:30:44,480
Come back here!

470
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,960
Come out now, Shooting Star!

471
00:30:46,960 --> 00:30:51,680
Shooting Star, I want to make a wish. Anna and Gao Bin are not allowed to get a divorce!

472
00:31:40,830 --> 00:31:46,990
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

473
00:31:46,990 --> 00:31:54,155
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

474
00:31:54,155 --> 00:32:00,245
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

475
00:32:00,245 --> 00:32:06,485
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

476
00:32:06,485 --> 00:32:13,037
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

477
00:32:13,037 --> 00:32:18,677
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

478
00:32:18,677 --> 00:32:22,590
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

479
00:32:22,590 --> 00:32:26,012
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

480
00:32:26,012 --> 00:32:29,307
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

481
00:32:29,307 --> 00:32:36,067
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

482
00:32:36,075 --> 00:32:39,278
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

483
00:32:39,278 --> 00:32:43,490
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

484
00:32:43,490 --> 00:32:47,310
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

485
00:32:47,310 --> 00:32:55,170
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
